|cFF00ccffAccount Unlock|r|nYou have joined forces with the Maruuk Centaurs on the Ohn'ahran Plains.

|cFF00ccffAccount Unlock|r|nYou have begun your adventures with the Dragonscale Expedition!

|cFF00ccffAccount Unlock|r|nSeek out Thaelin Darkanvil at the Rubyscale Outpost up the hill from the Dragonscale Basecamp to pursue access to a third Ancient Waygate.
|cFF00ccffAccount Unlock|r|nYou may acquire the cosmetic weapon appearances Excavator's Mallet, Excavator's Punch, Excavator's Chisel, and Excavator's Trowel from Rae'ana at the Dragonscale Basecamp.
